OL,6,FThe number of countries on that list
OL,7,Fhas been dwindling in recent years as
OL,8,FBeijing has encouraged country after
OL,9,Fcountry to break off diplomatic
OL,10,Frelations with Taipei and officially
OL,11,Frecognise 'One China'.
OL,13,FThe latest was Nauru, a tiny island in
OL,14,FMicronesia, which defected following
OL,15,FPresident Lai's election in January.
OL,17,FFor the next four years, President Lai
OL,18,Fis going to be walking a tight
OL,19,Fgeopolitical tightrope. He has placed
OL,20,Fhimself firmly in China's crosshairs.
